These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, poker, go, canasta
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, folk, jazz, salsa
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the fan jazz##1
2. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
3. the fan jazz is between the fan folk and the person playing poker##2
4. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
5. the person playing go is between the person playing poker and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | canasta         | poker   | go | monopoly       |
| Music-Genre      | salsa | indie | jazz   | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, disco, jazz, r&b
City: nizza, new-york, prague, hannover
1. the person traveling to hannover is between the fan jazz and the person traveling to new-york##2
2. the fan r&b is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the fan metal is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Music-Genre         | disco | metal | jazz | r&b |
| City   | new-york    | hannover   | nizza | prague       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, documentary, spy, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, sailing, lacrosse, swimming
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person watching documentary movies##2
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | epic    | western | documentary   | spy  |
| Sport   | sailing | lacrosse   | swimming | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
City: paris, london, colone, hamburg
House: townhouse, palace, gothic-revival, colonial
1. the palace house is the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to paris is between the townhouse house and the person traveling to hamburg##2
3. the palace house is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| City     | hamburg   | paris    | colone       | london   |
| House   | gothic-revival | colonial | townhouse | palace |

