.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, iris, amaryllis, begonia
City: marseilles, rome, london, boston
1. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to rome##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Flower   | lily        | amaryllis | begonia  | iris |
| City      | london | rome  | boston | marseilles    |

