.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, tram, motorbike
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, dancer, writer, musician
1. the writer is on the right of the dancer##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is the writer##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the electrician##1
5. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Transport   | scooter     | tram           | roller | motorbike  |
| Job         | electrician | musician | dancer   | writer |

