.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, cain, siglo, oliveros
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, dutch, polish
1. the cain-smoker is the british##1
2. the dutch is on the left of the british##1
3. the polish is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the indonesian is on the left of the polish##1
5. the ritmeester-smoker is between the british and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | oliveros   | cain | ritmeester | siglo      |
| Nationality     | dutch | british    | indonesian  | polish |

