.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, alhambra, baccarat
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, chinchilla, horse
1. the owner of the rat is the game-smoker##1
2. the owner of the turtle is between the alhambra-smoker and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar       | ritmeester | baccarat | alhambra     | game   |
| Pet   | chinchilla   | turtle     | horse | rat |

