.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, drawing, writing, board-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, marigold, poppy
1. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who growstulip and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Hobby         | drawing | writing | card-games | board-games |
| Flower   | tulip         | poppy       | aconite    | marigold         |

