.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, van, tram
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, marigold, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who growsrose is between the person driving the scooter and the person who growsballoon-flower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Transport    | tram   | van      | scooter   | roller  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | rose | marigold | iris |

