.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, march, may, july
City: berlin, liverpool, marseilles, rome
1. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in september##2
3. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Birthday          | september     | march | july   | may        |
| City   | berlin | marseilles   | liverpool | rome |

