.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, prince, swisher, dunhill
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, videographer, dressmaker, bartender
1. the dressmaker is the prince-smoker##1
2. the videographer is on the left of the bartender##1
3. the freelancer is the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the swisher-smoker is the videographer##1
5. the freelancer is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
6. the videographer is between the prince-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | prince | swisher | dunhill | dannemann |
| Job   | dressmaker          | videographer     | bartender  | freelancer     |

