4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, rabbit, pony
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is between the owner of the pony and the chaman-smoker##2
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | chaman | bolivar | blend | pall-mall     |
| Pet   | chinchilla   | rabbit    | pony   | guinea-pig |

