.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-14::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, rose, amaryllis, iris
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, singing, collecting, rock-climbing
1. the person who growsrose is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is singing##2
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | iris | amaryllis | rose |
| Hobby   | singing   | hiking | rock-climbing         | collecting |

