.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, indonesian, australian, argentine
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, lilac, aquamarine, grey
1. the person who likes brown is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the argentine is between the person who likes grey and the nigerian##2
3. the indonesian is on the right of the argentine##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |      4       |
| Nationality         | nigerian      | argentine | indonesian  | australian |
| Color   | lilac | aquamarine  | grey | brown    |

