.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, fanta, almond-milk
City: miami, rome, liverpool, nizza
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person drinking fanta is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person drinking water##2
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage   | cola | water | fanta | almond-milk |
| City     | miami     | rome   | nizza | liverpool  |

