.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
House: art-deco, modern, victorian, cottage
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, azure, green, amber
1. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the cottage house is the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes white and the modern house##2
4. the person who likes amber is the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| House   | cottage | modern | art-deco | victorian |
| Color           | green  | amber  | azure | white      |

