.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, almond-milk, mirinda
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, fonseca, aristoff, montecristo
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is the blend-smoker##1
4. the montecristo-smoker is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | mirinda   | milk   | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| Cigar         | blend | fonseca | montecristo     | aristoff    |

