.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, nigerian, indonesian, argentine
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, chaman, game, bluemaster
1. the chaman-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the spanish is between the baccarat-smoker and the argentine##2
3. the argentine is on the left of the spanish##1
4. the nigerian is on the far right##1
5. the nigerian is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | argentine     | spanish | nigerian |
| Cigar     | chaman | bluemaster | game       | baccarat     |

 